    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">08</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Frontier Challenges Word Cloud</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Identifying Key Challenges Faced by Texicans</h2><ul><li>Isolation and limited infrastructure</li><li>Threats from Native American raids</li><li>Legal and cultural tensions with Mexican authorities</li><li>Harsh environmental conditions</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">A word cloud activity synthesizes the multifaceted challenges Texicans encountered on the frontier, integrating social, political, and environmental factors (s8, s9). <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s8\">[8]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s9\">[9]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Words like 'raids,' 'isolation,' and 'cultural conflict' emerge prominently, reflecting core frontier issues.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Reflect on which challenges would most impact daily life and community cohesion.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Oversimplifying frontier life as only physically dangerous without social or political complexity.</p></div></div>",
